s/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係，胃口好咗，啱啱戒個排，真係好似餓鬼咁，食極唔飽，去邊度食飯都要加飯"},{"pid":"5d899d240974ee42f94ff0d9fb2ba369f80a583c","tid":567741,"uid":37413,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T16:39:40.000Z","msg":"戒完做番運動條氣順番晒<br />\n以前講嘢有時會唔夠氣走音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上樓梯都索晒氣，仲有胸口有時會痛<br />\n戒完乜都無晒啦"},{"pid":"271b0a47ee794cdaccb1ab9d5e9b4eb7c0c2b767","tid":567741,"uid":68764,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T21:50:59.000Z","msg":"戒左兩個月 除左慳返煙錢同無陣煙味之外無分別<br />\n有時覺得空虛左呢下真 <br />\n可能有時食支煙個時係發下吽哣 諗下野<br />\n而家無左呢啲時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe30fc4c3c0630557742b7fdc0986df7fd0d7c96","tid":567741,"uid":96146,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T22:00:29.000Z","msg":"前排因為成日覺得呼吸困難 開始想戒煙 <br />\n但我認自制能力低 而且最近真係好大壓力 更加戒唔到<br />\n所以轉左食電子煙<br />\n<br />\n不過轉左後 真係覺得抖氣順左 食既次數少左 <br />\n冇左個種想煙博煙既感覺 <br />\n由之前一日一包 減少到2日1包<br />\n希望之後能夠慢慢減 最終唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57cb1c259578a11d88cdfb2b2db11366d0e56bd6","tid":567741,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe30fc4c3c0630557742b7fdc0986df7fd0d7c96","tid":567741,"uid":96146,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T22:00:29.000Z","msg":"前排因為成日覺得呼吸困難 開始想戒煙 <br />\n但我認自制能力低 而且最近真係好大壓力 更加戒唔到<br />\n所以轉左食電子煙<br />\n<br />\n不過轉左後 真係覺得抖氣順左 食既次數少左 <br />\n冇左個種想煙博煙既感覺 <br />\n由之前一日一包 減少到2日1包<br />\n希望之後能夠慢慢減 最終唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T00:19:44.000Z","msg":"Em...<br />\n夜啦"},{"pid":"59eea7deaf845715e7262f5024a5b4bcff55e59d","tid":567741,"uid":122177,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T00:22:12.000Z","msg":"食左10年，戒咗三年，每日食十支左右。<br />\n利申：係仲戒緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8fb658b90769d5b7b75adc1018e0e7b8e58385e","tid":567741,"uid":17964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T00:29:47.000Z","msg":"食左三年<br />\n戒左大半年<br />\n條氣順左，冇再乾咳<br />\n一個月多左洗費 (呢到$180港紙一包萬寶路)<br />\n<br />\n但有時夜晚訓唔著都會好空虛<br />\n好想食返枝"},{"pid":"347778a417b05ca4a01892f42ea48436673792a3","tid":567741,"uid":57835,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T00:50:59.000Z","msg":"咁我唔食返啦<br />\n仲有一盒戒煙香口珠，兩百幾蚊，送畀巴打有無人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fadbab30a6ac8661c9c02881961990796e18bb3b","tid":567741,"uid":164896,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T02:22:52.000Z","msg":"食咗三十年煙,平均ㄧ日ㄧ包至包半,最近啱啱戒咗一個月,無靠葯物戒,純靠意志,希望可以繼續忍住!"},{"pid":"2222bbd82ab6af95a326c000485f7e166162c94f","tid":567741,"uid":18310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T02:24:26.000Z","msg":"食左十幾年，戒左幾年，好氣左，老母都打死幾個"},{"pid":"964f142eed0855d829834b5547cbf4917b18ccd3","tid":567741,"uid":119366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"347778a417b05ca4a01892f42ea48436673792a3","tid":567741,"uid":57835,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T00:50:59.000Z","msg":"咁我唔食返啦<br />\n仲有一盒戒煙香口珠，兩百幾蚊，送畀巴打有無人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T02:43:02.000Z","msg":"戒左就唔好食返啦，屎忽痕咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ffb9c66e48954b8a153102f089b96f2173ba94","tid":567741,"uid":47147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T02:49:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b5e32199ebf65a0ed8e5f28f73b325241256774","tid":567741,"uid":90839,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e5ffb9c66e48954b8a153102f089b96f2173ba94","tid":567741,"uid":47147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T02:49:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-